      <li>
        <strong>Manage my rides</strong> – A platform to organize and track motorcycle rides.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Flucky</strong> – A fun, interactive web app for random selections and games.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Eat healthy store</strong> – An e-commerce solution for healthy food products.
